(81, 1, '2025-09-28 14:19:37', '2025-09-28 14:19:37', '<p dir=\"auto\">Protect your iPhone 12 with the Spigen Ultra Hybrid Case, a perfect blend of style and durability. Crafted with a clear TPU and polycarbonate hybrid design, this case showcases your phone\'s original color while offering reliable 10ft drop protection. Featuring precise cutouts for easy access, anti-yellowing technology for long-lasting clarity, and full MagSafe compatibility, its ideal for wireless charging enthusiasts. Slim yet sturdy, this case ensures your device stays safe and stylish every day.</p>', 'iPhone 12 Cases', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', '3-speed-bike', '', '', '2025-09-29 19:07:02', '2025-09-29 19:07:02', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/index.php/product/3-speed-bike/', 0, 'product', '', 0),
